nah i got it mostly to work heres how to do it for you windows 7 people

1.install the game with daemon tools
2. un pack the crack in the gangland crack folder with Win raw use the "extract" option.
3.that coppys it to a folder on your desktop open the folder and drag the icon that should say "Gangland Exe." to program files and whereever you installed gangland drop it where you see another "gangland exe" replace it.
4. REMBER without the crack the game DOES NOT WORK.
5. then right click the shortcut to gangland and go to properties, go to the Compatibility tab and check the 4 bottom boxes not the first 3. the first box you see says "Run this program in compatibilty mode for:" check it and go to windows 2000.
6.after that start up the game it should ask you the serial code but for the life of me i dont know how to put it in right.
7.if you figure out the serial code have fun!

never mind you wont belive how to fix the serial key problem, you have to disable your protection the game uses a mini keylogger to see if you put in the right code just disable your protection to put in the serial key and BAM it works lol make shure you exit out turn on your anti virus and then go back on, so you dont get viruses.i had kesperskey and i saw out of the cornor of my eye that it said "gangland mimic's behavior of keylogger" and i just connected the two. so there you have it how to play gangland. took alot of room but im shure people will thank me later! lol
